            <td>Memory</td>
            <td>No minimum requirement. The necessary amount of memory needed by Doelan depends on size of the files to be tested. Currently with GPR and GAL files greater than 20,000 lines, Doelan doesn't need to modify the memory allocation pool size (default is 64 MiB) with the <b>-Xmx</b> option of the JVM.</td>
